OL,6,FThe layby has been closed while
OL,7,Fspecialist contractors carry out the
OL,8,Fclearance.
OL,10,FCouncillor Richard Millard, Leader of
OL,11,FEHDC, said: "Fly-tipping is a
OL,12,Fdisgraceful crime that wrecks our
OL,13,Fenvironment, endangers public health
OL,14,Fand drains vital resources.
OL,16,F"Every pound spent clearing up this
OL,17,Fmess is a pound stolen from essential
OL,18,Fservices that support our residents.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
