OL,6,F"We will not tolerate it. Our teams
OL,7,Finvestigate every single incident,
OL,8,Fhunting for evidence to catch the
OL,9,Fculprits.
OL,11,F"Anyone who takes such selfish,
OL,12,Fillegal actions are parasites on
OL,13,Fsociety.
OL,15,F"So, if you dump waste, we will do
OL,16,Feverything in our power to find you
OL,17,Fand prosecute you to the full extent
OL,18,Fof the law."
