OL,6,FHe added: "But don't forget, we all
OL,7,Fhave a part to play in stopping vile
OL,8,Ffly-tips like this.
OL,10,F"If your waste ends up in a fly-tip
OL,11,Fand you haven't done your due
OL,12,Fdiligence, you will be held
OL,13,Faccountable.
OL,15,F"So make sure you do your duty.
OL,17,F"Check your waste collector's
OL,18,Fcredentials. Demand a waste carrier's
OL,19,Flicence and a disposal receipt.
